{
  "stem": "6258.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The last battle during the Second World War, it was probably there where I was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the German took me down to the basement, the peasant, and I was sitting there with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, what an irony.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Here, if something will, well, bang at this house, I will be dead with two Germans, and nobody will know about it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But nothing was happening, except that suddenly the German run away, the soldiers who were there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we hear steps, and some [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] And I knew that no German speaks that way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I banged up, and there was a very tired Russian soldier.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I jump on him, and embrace him, and I start crying, and he was afraid of me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was, what do you want, you German woman?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, no, I am not-- and I show him this, and he said, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], I know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, at this moment, he said, Auschwitz, and I knew that he knew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was with this German peasant for about three days or four days while I was working for them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, taking care of cows, and this, and that, and that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And anyway, he just asked, were they good?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they were not good, I will kill him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was just looking at them, and I know that under my bed there was a suitcase.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in this suitcase was a Gestapo uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was room of their son.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, this is strange.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it takes about half a minute.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything in my mind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Why do I care about them?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Perhaps their son was killing my father, or beating, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
